text: This obsoletes IRM 20.2.6, Interest, Methods of Computing Interest.

Content from IRM 20.2.6, Interest, Methods of Computing Interest, is incorporated and changed in IRM 20.2.1, Interest, Interest Introduction, Standards and Guidelines, which transmits a complete revision of the former IRM 20.2.1, Interest, General and Legal Authorizations, IRM 20.2.5, Interest, Interest on Underpayments, and IRM 20.2.7, Interest, Abatement and Suspension of Debit Interest. Content from IRM 20.2.6, Interest: Methods of Computing Interest, is tracked in the following table.

Subsection (MM-DD-YYYY)New Location IRM 20.2.6.9, Helpful Interest IRM 20.2.1.4, Types of Interest; Facts IRM 20.2.5.1, Underpayment Interest; IRM 20.2.5.6, Restricted Interest; IRM 20.2.7.8, IRC 6601(c) Suspension of Interest on Deficiencies
This IRM is intended for employees of all operating divisions who work with interest.
